commit.message:
[checker] Cut all dependencies from `engine/library`.

These are ~5000 less of dependencies in exchange of adding 20, so IMO
the tradeoff is clear, in particular due to the status of the imported
libs.

Note there was some strange stuff regarding `engage`.
